\c 27
\s Jakobho anoropafadzwa pachigaro chaEsau
\p
\v 1 Zvino Isaka wakati ava mutana, meso ake owonera madzedzerere, asisaoni zvakanaka, akadana Esau, mwa­nakomana wake mukuru, akati kwaari, Mwana wangu; iye akati kwaari, Ndiri pano hangu.
\v 2 Akati, Tarira zvino ndakwegura; handizivi zuva rokufa kwangu.
\v 3 Zvino tora hako nhumbi dzako dzokuvhima nadzo, dzinoti goba rako, nouta hwako, uende kusango undivhimire mhuka;
\v 4 undigadzirire nyama yakanaka, sezvandinoda, uuye nayo kwandiri, ndi­dye, mweya wangu ukuropafadze, ndisati ndafa.
\p
\v 5 Zvino Rabheka akanzwa Isaka achitaura naEsau, mwanakomana wake. Esau akaenda kusango kundovhima mhuka, kuti auye nayo.
\v 6 Rabheka aka­taura naJakobho, mwanakomana wake, akati, Tarira, ndanzwa baba vako va­chitaura naEsau, mukoma wako, vachiti,
\v 7 Nditorere mhuka, undigadzirire nyama yakanaka, kuti ndiidye, ndikuro­pafadze pamberi paJehovha ndisati ndafa.
\v 8 Zvino mwana wangu, teerera inzwi rangu sezvandinokuraira.
\v 9 Enda zvino kuzvipfuwo, unditorerepo mbu­dzana mbiri dzakanaka, ndigadzirire baba vako nadzo nyama yakanaka, se­zvavanoda;
\v 10 ugoenda nayo kuna baba vako, vadye, kuti vakuropafadze vasati vafa.
\v 11 Jakobho akati kuna Rabheka mai vake, Tarirai, Esau, mukoma wa­ngu, munhu ane mvere, asi ini ndiri munhu asina mvere.
\v 12 Zvimwe baba vangu vachandibata-bata, ndikava so­munyengedzeri pamberi pavo, ndika­zviuyisira kutukwa pachigaro chokuro­pafadzwa.
\p
\v 13 Mai vake vakati kwaari, Kutukwa kwako ngakuve pamusoro pangu, mwana wangu; teerera hako inzwi rangu, uende unditorere idzo.
\v 14 Iye akaenda, akadzi­tora, akadziisa kuna mai vake; mai vake vakagadzira nyama yakanaka, yaidika­mwa nababa vake.
\v 15 Zvino Rabheka akatora nguvo dzakaisvonaka dzaEsau, mwa­nakomana wake mukuru, dzaaiva nadzo mumba, akadzifukidza Jakobho, mwana­komana wake muduku;
\v 16 akaisa nguvo dzembudzana pamaoko ake, napamutsipa wake pakanga pasina mvere;
\v 17 akaisa nyama yakanaka nechingwa, zvaakanga agadzira, muruoko rwaJakobho, mwana­komana wake.
\p
\v 18 Iye akaenda kuna baba vake, akati, Baba vangu; ivo vakati, Ndiri pano hangu; ndiwe aniko mwana wangu?
\v 19 Jakobho akati kuna baba vake, Ndini Esau, dangwe renyu; ndaita sezvamandi­raira; mukai henyu, mugare, mudye nyama yangu yemhuka, mweya wenyu undiropafadze.
\p
\v 20 Isaka akati kumwanakomana wake, Wakurumidza seiko kuiwana, mwana wangu? Iye akati, nekuti Jeho­vha, Mwari wenyu, waituma pamberi pangu.
\p
\v 21 Isaka akati kuna Jakobho, Chi­mboswedera hako, ndikubate-bate, mwana wangu, kuti ndizive kuti uri mwanakomana wangu Esau chaiye, kana kuti hausi iwe.
\v 22 Jakobho akaswedera kuna Isaka, baba vake; ivo vakamubata­bata, vakati, Inzwi, inzwi raJakobho, asi maoko maoko aEsau.
\v 23 Asi haana kumu­ziva, nekuti maoko ake akanga aine mvere, samaoko omukuru wake Esau; akamuropafadza.
\v 24 Akati, Ndiwe mwa­nakomana wangu Esau chaiye here? Iye akati, Ndini iye.
\p
\v 25 Akati, Uiswededze pedo neni, kuti ndidye nyama yemhuka yomwana­komana wangu, mweya wangu ukuropa­fadze. Iye akaiswededza pedo naye, akadya; akamupawo waini, akamwa.
\v 26 Ipapo baba vake Isaka vakati kwaari, Swedera zvino unditsvode, mwana wa­ngu.
\v 27 Akaswedera, akamutsvoda; aka­nzwa munhuwi wenguvo dzake, akamuro­pafadzwa, akati, Tarira munhuwi womwanakomana wangu wakaita somunhuwi wesango rakaropafadzwa naJehovha;
\v 28 Mwari ngaakupe dova rokudenga, mafuta enyika, nezviyo newaini zvakawanda.
\v 29 Vanhu ngavakushumire, marudzi ose ngaakupfugamire; uve ishe wehama dzako, vanakomana vamai vako ngavakupfugamire; vose vanokutuka ngavatukwe, vose vanokuropafadza ngavaropafadzwe.
\p
\v 30 Zvino Isaka wakati apedza kuropa­fadza Jakobho, Jakobho achangobuda pamberi palsaka baba vake, Esau mu­koma wake, akapinda, achibva paku­vhima kwake.
\v 31 Naiye akagadzira nyama yakanaka, akaenda nayo kuna baba vake; akati kuna baba vake, Baba vangu ngavamuke, ngavadye nyama yemhuka yomwanakomana wavo, kuti mweya we­nyu undiropafadze.
\p
\v 32 Ipapo Isaka baba vake vakati, Ndiwe aniko? Iye akati, Ndini mwa­nakomana wenyu, dangwe renyu Esau.
\v 33 Isaka akabvunda kwazvo-kwazvo, akati, Ndianiko wakanga avhima mhuka, akauya nayo kwandiri ndikadya zvose, iwe usati wasvika, ndikamuropa­fadza? Hongu, zvirokwazvo iye acharo­pafadzwa hake.
\p
\v 34 Esau akati achinzwa mashoko ababa vake, akachema nokuchema ku­kuru kunorwadza moyo, akati kuna baba vake, Ndiropafadzei neniwo, baba vangu!
\p
\v 35 Akati, Munun'una wako wakauya nokunyengedzera, akatora kuropafadzwa kwako.
\p
\v 36 Iye akati, Haana kutumidzwa zita rakamufanira here, rokuti Jakobho? No­kuti zvino wandinyengedzera kaviri; wa­mbonditorera udangwe hwangu, zvino tarira, wanditorera kuropafadzwa kwa­ngu. Akati, Hamuna kundichengete­rawo kuropafadzwa here?
\p
\v 37 Isaka akapindura, akati kuna Esau, Tarira, ndamuita ishe wako, nehama dzake dzose ndakamupa iye, kuti vave varanda vake; ndamusimbisa nezviyo ne­waini; zvino chinyiko chandingakuitira iwe, mwana wangu?
\p
\v 38 Esau akati kuna baba vake, Mu­nongova nokuropafadza kumwe koga here, baba vangu? Ndiropafadzei, ne­niwo, baba vangu! Esau akachema no­kuchema. kukuru.
\v 39 Ipapo Isaka baba vake, akapindura akati kwaari, Tarira, ugaro hwako uchava kure namafuta enyika, kure nedova rokudenga rinobva kumusoro;
\v 40 uchararama nomunondo wako, uchashumira munun'una wako; uchati kana wozvimutsa iwe, uchavhuna joko rake ribve pamutsipa wako.
\p
\v 41 Esau akavenga Jakobho nokuda kokuropafadzwa kwaakaropafadzwa nako nababa vake; Esau akati mumoyo make, Mazuva okuchema baba vangu ava kuda kusvika; ipapo ndichauraya munun'una wangu Jakobho.
\p
\v 42 Zvino Rabheka akaudzwa ma­shoko aEsau, mwanakomana wake mu­kuru; akatuma munhu kundodana Jako­bho, mwanakomana wake muduku, akati kwaari, Tarira, mukoma wako Esau anozvivaraidza pamusoro pako, achiti achakuuraya.
\v 43 Saka zvino, mwana wa­ngu, teerera inzwi rangu; simuka utizire Harani kuna Rabhani hanzvadzi yangu;
\v 44 undogara kwaari mazuva mashoma­nana, kusvikira shungu dzomukoma wako dzanyarara;
\v 45 kusvikira kutsamwa komukoma wako kwanyarara kwauri, kana akangamwa izvo zvawamuitira. Ipapo ndichatuma munhu kuzokutora ikoko; ndichatorerwa seiko nomusi mu­mwe imwi mose muri vaviri?
\v 46 Rabheka akati kuna Isaka, Ndanetswa noupenyu hwangu nokuda kwavakunda vaHeti; kana Jakobho akawanawo mukadzi ku­vakunda vaHeti, wakaita saivava, kuva­kunda venyika ino, upenyu hwangu ungandibatsirei?
